---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import scottImg from '../../images/scott-murray.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="I'm Scott — a traveler who fell in love with Colorado's mountains, ski towns, and wide-open spaces. This is my story and why I built Discover Colorado."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="bg-[#1A2332] text-white text-center py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#D4A574] mb-6">About Discover Colorado</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6">Mountains, Memories &amp; Miles of Road</h1>
    <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">I'm Scott — a healthcare IT professional from San Diego who has spent years exploring Colorado's peaks, ski towns, and hidden gems. This site is everything I've learned, documented for anyone planning their own Colorado adventure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- My Story -->
<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="border-l-2 border-[#EBE4D8] hover:border-[#0D7377] transition-colors pl-8">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[#E8654A] mb-3">Scott <span class="text-gray-500 font-normal tracking-[0.05em]">· Traveler · Writer · Based in San Diego</span></p>
    <p class="text-[#1A2332] leading-[2] font-light">
      Colorado grabbed me on my first trip — driving I-70 west from Denver, watching the Front Range rise up, and realizing that this state has everything from world-class skiing to craft beer scenes that rival any city in America. Since then I've been back more times than I can count, each trip going deeper: Telluride's box canyon, the sand dunes at Great Sand Dunes, the hot springs in Ouray, the empty highways of the Western Slope.<br><br>
      <strong>I'm not a travel blogger. I work in healthcare IT.</strong> But Colorado keeps pulling me back, and I decided to put everything I've learned into something useful — a site with real logistics, honest prices, and the kind of detail you only get from someone who has actually driven those mountain passes and waited in those lift lines. Discover Colorado is the resource I wished existed when I was planning my first trip west.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Profile Card -->
<section class="bg-[#F5F0E8] py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
      <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c3547] via-[#0D7377] to-[#14B8A6]"></div>
      <Image src={scottImg} alt="Scott Murray" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-4 border-white mx-auto -mt-12 relative z-10 object-cover shadow-lg" width={96} height={96} format="webp" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="px-8 pb-8 pt-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A2332] mb-1">Scott</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-5">Founder · Writer · The Outsider's Perspective</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#4A5568] leading-relaxed text-left font-light">Based in Southern California. Healthcare IT by day, Colorado travel obsessive by every other waking moment. Started as weekend ski trips that turned into week-long road trips covering every corner of the state. Now documenting it all — real prices, real routes, honest opinions.</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 pt-5 mt-5 border-t border-[#F5F0E8]">
          <div class="text-center"><div class="font-serif text-xl text-[#1A2332]">10+</div><div class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 mt-1">Years exploring CO</div></div>
          <div class="text-center"><div class="font-serif text-xl text-[#1A2332]">20+</div><div class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 mt-1">Trips & counting</div></div>
          <div class="text-center"><div class="font-serif text-xl text-[#1A2332]">40+</div><div class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 mt-1">Countries traveled</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Promise -->
<section class="bg-[#1A2332] py-20 px-6 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#D4A574] mb-3">Our Promise</p>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-white mb-8">What You Won't Find Here</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light mb-12">I built this site because I got tired of Colorado travel content that's secretly a press trip recap or a sponsored hotel review. Discover Colorado exists because I wanted the resource I wished I had.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white/[0.035] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-6"><div class="font-serif text-4xl text-[#E8654A] mb-2">0</div><div class="text-xs text-white/40">Sponsored posts<br>ever</div></div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.035] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-6"><div class="font-serif text-4xl text-[#11969B] mb-2">0</div><div class="text-xs text-white/40">Press trips or<br>free hotel stays</div></div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.035] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-6"><div class="font-serif text-4xl text-[#D4A574] mb-2">10+</div><div class="text-xs text-white/40">Years of Colorado<br>experience</div></div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.035] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-6"><div class="font-serif text-4xl text-white mb-2">100%</div><div class="text-xs text-white/40">Real prices<br>in USD</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="bg-[#0D7377] py-16 px-6 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-white mb-3">Start Exploring Colorado</h2>
    <p class="text-white/70 font-light mb-8">20 destination guides with real prices, honest opinions, and insider tips.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/destinations/" class="bg-[#E8654A] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#D4553B] transition-colors">Browse Destinations</a>
      <a href="/plan/" class="border-2 border-white/60 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">AI Trip Planner</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
